Package: whitesur-gtk-themes
Architecture: all
Depends: whitesur-dark-gtk-theme,
 whitesur-light-gtk-theme,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: A macOS BigSur-like theme for your GTK apps
 Make your desktop look beautiful with this GTK theme inspired on MacOS design,
 it works on Gnome, XFCE and any other desktop environment that uses GTK.

